<span class="displaytext">arlington, va -- today, (candidate last)-palin 2008 released its latest radio ad, entitled "stem cell response." the ad is in response to (candidate full)'s "false" and "misleading" radio ad on stem cell research. (candidate full) is proud to have a record of supporting stem cell research and will continue to fight for this vital research as president. <b> </b><p>listen to the ad here: <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fug_5bqkoyq">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fug_5bqkoyq</a> <b><u> </u></b></p><p>script for "stem cell response" (radio :60) <i> </i></p><p>anncr: (candidate full) and his congressional allies' stem cell attacks are simply not true. </p><p>leading news organizations call their attacks "misleading." "out of bounds." "manhandling the truth." "wrong." </p><p>the truth? </p><p>(candidate full) and his congressional allies fought for stem cell research. </p><p>they stood up and said stem cell research was too important for you and your family. </p><p>stem cell research will help unlock the mystery of cancer, diabetes and heart disease. it will allow scientists to explore treatment for parkinson's and alzheimer's. </p><p>stem cell research will help free families from the fear and devastation of illness. </p><p>change is coming. (candidate last)-palin and congressional allies. </p><p>the leadership and experience to change washington and improve your health. </p><p>paid for by (candidate last)-palin 2008 and the (PARTY NAME) national committee. <b> </b></p><p>(candidate full): i'm (candidate full) and i approve this message. <b><u> </u></b></p><p>ad facts: script for "stem cell response" (radio :60) <i> </i></p><p>anncr: (candidate full) and his congressional allies' stem cell attacks are simply not true. leading news organizations call their attacks "misleading." "out of bounds." "manhandling the truth." "wrong." <b> </b></p><p>abc news: (candidate full)'s stem cell ad is "misleading." "thus, when (candidate last)'s radio a